headline: Lazard Reports 1.7% Sequential AUM Growth in May on Market Gains
summary: LAZ posts 1.7% AUM growth in May to $235.3 billion, lifted by upbeat markets despite $3.7 billion in net outflows and a $4.3 billion client withdrawal.
